I reduced a bit the difficulty on the second trap (the glass one) a lot of people were dying here , and it is supposed to be an "easy trap"

Some "nodraw" textures were visible , just a little fix.

Added 3 "trail grenades"

Added some details like blood and corpses.

Thanks to Jean-Baboule , and the TLD server for the live testing :)
